WEBVTT

00:01.320 --> 00:02.988
Good morning, Ron.

00:03.031 --> 00:05.499
Good morning.

00:05.566 --> 00:08.568
I know how much you enjoy
paperwork, but don't hover.

00:08.620 --> 00:10.120
Nice bench.
Is that new?

00:10.205 --> 00:12.806
No, that's been there
since the '90s.

00:12.874 --> 00:14.541
What are you doing
for your birthday on Friday?

00:14.592 --> 00:17.211
Nothing.
I never d...

00:17.262 --> 00:19.446
- Aha!
- Oh, God.

00:19.514 --> 00:21.215
♪ Birthday,
birthday, birthday ♪

00:21.282 --> 00:23.217
♪ it's your birthday ♪

00:23.284 --> 00:25.152
♪ it's your birthday,
and I know when it is ♪

00:25.220 --> 00:28.255
Ron refuses to tell anyone
when his birthday is.

00:28.323 --> 00:31.158
He's even had it redacted
on all government documents.

00:31.225 --> 00:34.077
Three years of investigations,
phone calls,

00:34.162 --> 00:36.230
Freedom of Information Act
requests,

00:36.297 --> 00:37.731
and still, I had nothing...

00:37.799 --> 00:42.369
Until a well-placed bribe to
a gentleman at Baskin-Robbins

00:42.437 --> 00:44.204
revealed...

00:44.272 --> 00:46.156
Ron's birthday is on Friday.

00:46.224 --> 00:48.025
Damn it.
I was so careful.

00:48.092 --> 00:49.176
Well, you blew it.

00:49.244 --> 00:51.428
All for a free scoop
of rum raisin.

00:51.513 --> 00:53.814
Was it worth it, Ron?
Was it?

00:53.882 --> 00:55.716
I command you to do nothing.

00:55.783 --> 00:57.718
I'm not gonna do nothing.
I'm gonna do something.

00:57.769 --> 00:58.936
And it's gonna be really big.

00:59.020 --> 01:00.888
I have a lot of years
to make up for.

01:00.939 --> 01:04.691
I don't like loud noises
and people making a fuss,

01:04.759 --> 01:07.327
and I especially
don't like people celebrating

01:07.395 --> 01:11.498
because they know a piece
of private information about me.

01:11.566 --> 01:13.634
Plus,
the whole thing is a scam.

01:13.701 --> 01:17.437
Birthdays were invented
by Hallmark to sell cards.

